.claude/worktrees/

# Phase-0 audit baseline traces — useful locally for before/after comparison
# but ~10 MB of Playwright trace zips that would bloat the repo. Re-capture
# locally via Phase 0 protocol when needed (docs/audit/00-baseline.md §2).
docs/audits/**/baseline-traces/
